    "The error bars and boxes representing statistical and systematic uncertainties indicate that the J∕ R AA remains constant from √ s NN = 17.3 GeV to 200 GeV and substantially increases from RHIC top energy to LHC.The curves in the left and right panels of Fig. 29 depict the calculations from two transport models [240,241].",
